{\fscx70\fscy70}...to recognize publicly...{\r}

877
01:32:30,327 --> 01:32:32,989
亨利·克萊格隊長那機智迅速的行動
{\fscx70\fscy70}...the intelligent and effective assistance...{\r}

878
01:32:33,163 --> 01:32:37,964
協助我和密蘇里州
