903
01:34:40,357 --> 01:34:42,587
你是迪克·利禿吧？
{\fscx70\fscy70}So you're Dick Little.{\r}

904
01:34:44,461 --> 01:34:45,985
利都
{\fscx70\fscy70}Liddil.{\r}

905
01:34:46,730 --> 01:34:48,664
什麼？
{\fscx70\fscy70}I beg your pardon?{\r}

906
01:34:48,965 --> 01:34:50,557
是d的音
{\fscx70\fscy70}I spell it with two D's.{\r}

907
01:34:50,734 --> 01:34:53,100
