a conditional pardon...{\r}

910
01:34:59,242 --> 01:35:03,110
赦免他犯的所有搶劫罪
{\fscx70\fscy70}...and amnesty for all the robberies
he's committed.{\r}

911
01:35:04,748 --> 01:35:05,976
你是羅伯特·福特？
