912
01:35:09,486 --> 01:35:10,783
多大了？
{\fscx70\fscy70}How old are you?{\r}

913
01:35:12,856 --> 01:35:14,289
二十
{\fscx70\fscy70}Twenty.{\r}

914
01:35:14,591 --> 01:35:17,116
你也向汀布萊克警長投降了？
{\fscx70\fscy70}You surrender to Sheriff Timberlake
as well?{\r}

915
01:35:17,294 --> 01:35:21,196
不是，他的哥哥查理·福特
才是詹姆斯匪幫的匪徒
{\fscx70\fscy70}No, no, governor. That's his brother,
Charley Ford, he's in the James Gang.{\r}

916
01:35:21,364 --> 01:35:24,094
和小鮑勃沒關係
{\fscx70\fscy70}But little Bob here,
we got nothing on Bob.{\r}

917
01:35:24,267 --> 01:35:26,827
他只是充當一個
{\fscx70\fscy70}He's just acting in capacity as a...{\r}

918
01:35:29,039 --> 01:35:31,200
秘密警探而已
{\fscx70\fscy70}...private detective.{\r}

919
01:35:32,375 --> 01:35:34,400
傑西·詹姆斯上個月給我打了個電報
