923
01:35:43,386 --> 01:35:45,320
我會先拆掉他的火車
{\fscx70\fscy70}I'll wreck his train first.{\r}

924
01:35:52,896 --> 01:35:57,060
抱歉，州長大人，我在想別的事情
{\fscx70\fscy70}I'm sorry, Your Excellency.
