than a public outlaw...{\r}

926
01:35:59,736 --> 01:36:02,534
打家劫舍，臭名遠揚
{\fscx70\fscy70}...who made his reputation
by stealing whatever he wanted...{\r}

927
01:36:02,706 --> 01:36:04,936
誰擋他的道就殺誰
{\fscx70\fscy70}...killing whoever got in his way.{\r}

928
01:36:05,108 --> 01:36:08,703
有的傻瓜說他是在報復
