is a desperate case...{\r}

934
01:36:25,762 --> 01:36:28,663
也需要極端的制裁
{\fscx70\fscy70}...and may require a desperate remedy.{\r}

935
01:36:32,002 --> 01:36:35,096
那您就找對人了
{\fscx70\fscy70}Y'all got the right man for the job.{\r}

936
01:36:51,454 --> 01:36:53,718
快走呀
{\fscx70\fscy70}Come on. Come on, now.{\r}

937
01:36:54,291 --> 01:36:55,918
快走
{\fscx70\fscy70}Come on, now.{\r}

938
01:37:40,303 --> 01:37:42,863
